![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2a76530d-650c-42bb-8439-d8521b00c4dc/20240415_003701.jpg)

In the wake of his departure from STARDOM, Rossy Ogawa, the mastermind behind the popular promotion, has wasted no time in embarking on his next venture. Recently ousted by the new owners BUSHIROAD, Ogawa is now charting his own path with the announcement of his new wrestling promotion, "Marigold."

The revelation of Marigold comes as no surprise to many in the wrestling community, who have been eagerly awaiting Ogawa's next move following his exit from STARDOM. With a track record of success and a keen eye for talent, Ogawa's new endeavor is already generating significant buzz.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8e068dd6-934b-42bc-8438-a796adb0f359/20240415_003807.jpg)

Alongside the announcement of the promotion's name, Ogawa also unveiled the initial roster for Marigold, showcasing a mix of established stars and up-and-coming talent. Among the names revealed are:

\- \*\*Giulia:\*\* Known for her fierce in-ring style and commanding presence, Giulia is sure to be a cornerstone of Marigold's roster.

\- \*\*Utami Hayashishita:\*\* Utami Hayashishita brings a combination of athleticism and technical prowess to Marigold.

\- \*\*MIRAI:\*\* With a name that speaks to the future, MIRAI promises to bring innovation and excitement to Marigold's events.

\- \*\*Mai Sakurai:\*\* A promising talent with a bright future ahead, Mai Sakurai's inclusion on the roster adds depth to Marigold's lineup.

\- \*\*Yuzuki:\*\* Little is known about Yuzuki at this time, but her presence on the roster suggests that she is poised to make an impact in Marigold.

\- \*\*Nanae Takahashi:\*\* A veteran of the wrestling world, Nanae Takahashi brings experience and leadership to Marigold's roster.

\- \*\*Nao Ishikawa:\*\* Rounding out the initial roster, Nao Ishikawa brings her own unique style and skills to Marigold.

With a roster boasting such diverse talent, Marigold is already shaping up to be a formidable force in the world of professional wrestling. As fans eagerly await further details about the promotion's plans and upcoming events, one thing is certain: Rossy Ogawa's Marigold is poised to make a significant impact on the wrestling landscape.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ff1cea45-8896-4043-a250-2395c84dfec7/20240415_022157.jpg)

In a stunning turn of events, Actwres girl'Z wrestling promotion has lost 6 wrestlers at once, including their main champion, to Rossy Ogawa's new Marigold promotion.

This includes senior member of staff Fuka, the promotion's main Champion, Natsumi Sumikawa and 5 other wrestlers.

Miku Aono

Misa Matsui

Kouki

Chiaki

Chika Goto

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/93f30fe6-4605-4dc4-94bc-0a6407d19594/20240415_004945.jpg)

The first Marigold show is on May 20th in the Korakuen Hall! It will air on Wrestle Universe with English and Japanese commentary

The first match is:

GIULIA & X vs. SAREE & X